io/basisDetail> ; <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#nodeKind> <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#IRI> . ?atInstant <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#path> <https://spectacular-voyage.github.io/stagecraft/ontology/perceptio/atInstant> ; <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#datatype> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> ; <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#minCount> \"1\"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#integer> ; <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#maxCount> \"1\"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#integer> . }",
